==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Devisable
<hw>De*vis"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Devise</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Capable of being devised,
invented, or contrived.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Capable of being bequeathed, or given by
will.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Devisal</ent>⟦br⟧
